SUMMARY:Deadline: Arte Laguna Prize 2026 (21st Edition)
DESCRIPTION:International Arte Laguna Prize\, open to artists across many m
 edia including dedicated digital art and video sections\, with a finalist 
 exhibition at the Venice Arsenale Nord. ELIGIBILITY: individual artists of
  all ages and nationalities worldwide. NOTE: an entry fee applies (roughly
  EUR 97 to EUR 122)\, but the prize awards substantial cash. Apply via the
  Arte Laguna Prize page.\n\nOrganisation: Arte Laguna (Venice)\nLocation: 
 Venice\, Italy (finalist exhibition at Arsenale Nord)\nAward: EUR 10\,000 
 main prize plus additional FOMAS prizes (EUR 7\,000 / 4\,000 / 3\,000) and
  a finalist exhibition at the Venice Arsenale Nord. Entry fee approximatel
 y EUR 97 to EUR 122.\nDuration: One-off prize\n\nMore: https://artelagunap
 rize.com/21-edition/
URL:https://artelagunaprize.com/21-edition/
LOCATION:Venice\, Italy (finalist exhibition at Arsenale Nord)
END:VEVENT
