SUMMARY:Deadline: Goethe-Institut: Individual Mobility Grants 2026 (Sub-Sah
 aran Africa and Europe)
DESCRIPTION:Goethe-Institut individual mobility grants for artists\, resear
 chers and curators (including digital and computational practitioners) for
  research\, collaboration\, residency placements or project development be
 tween Sub-Saharan Africa and Europe. ELIGIBILITY: individual artists\, res
 earchers and cultural workers. QUARTERLY DEADLINES: 15 June 2026\, 15 Sept
 ember 2026 and 15 December 2026.\n\nOrganisation: Goethe-Institut\nLocatio
 n: Mobility between Sub-Saharan Africa and Europe\nAward: Travel costs up 
 to EUR 1\,800 (from Europe)\, accommodation\, daily allowances and project
  expenses covered. No application fee.\nDuration: Project-based mobility (
 variable length)\n\nMore: https://www.goethe.de/prj/aep/en/cal/ssa/mga/img
 .html
