DTSTAMP:20260525T190820Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260521
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260522
SUMMARY:Deadline: VIA Art Fund: Artistic Production Grant (Fall 2026 cycle)
DESCRIPTION:Production grants for newly commissioned works of visual art ex
 hibited beyond museum walls\, in the public realm\, or in non-traditional 
 exhibition environments. Grants are awarded to projects that best exemplif
 y VIA's three core values of Artistic Production\, Thought Leadership\, an
 d Public Engagement. Two-stage application process: Letter of Inquiry due 
 21 May 2026\; invitations to submit a full application sent 24 June 2026 (
 by invitation only)\; full application deadline for invited applicants 23 
 July 2026\; grant award notification November 2026. Projects must start af
 ter 15 December 2026. VIA runs Fall and Spring cycles each year\; Fall 202
 6 is the current open call.\n\nOrganisation: VIA Art Fund\nLocation: World
 wide (projects exhibited beyond museum walls\, in the public realm\, or in
  non-traditional exhibition environments)\nAward: $25\,000 to $100\,000 pe
 r project\nDuration: Per project (must start after 15 December 2026)\n\nMo
 re: https://viaartfund.org/apply/
URL:https://viaartfund.org/apply/
LOCATION:Worldwide (projects exhibited beyond museum walls\, in the public 
 realm\, or in non-traditional exhibition environments)
END:VEVENT
